title: Validation and upgrading of the recommended cross section data of charged particle reactions: Gamma emitter radioisotopes

x4freetext: Validation and upgrading of the recommended  cross
section data of charged particle reactions: Gamma

x4codes.hlp: Institute for Nuclear Research (ATOMKI), Debrecen, Hungary

x4codes.shortRef: Jour: Nucl. Instrum. Methods in Physics Res., Sect.B, Vol.240, p.790 (2005)

x4freetext: Experimental data were collected and critically
selected for each of the reactions. Recommended cross
section data sets were created by using statistical fit
over the selected data. Recommended thick target yields
physical yields or saturation yields were calculated
from the recommended cross sections and the stopping
power published by Andersen and Ziegler (see REL-REF).
